Pebble Camera take a PHOTO or VIDEO on your phone through your Pebble! With LIVE PREVIEW on Pebble!
• Camera facing (Front or Back);
• Photo / Video resolution;
• Flash mode;
• Self-timer;
• Quality preview.
You can also use this app as a Spy Camera, it can take photos or videos without any sound or light! Put your phone somewhere, no further than 10 meters from Pebble.

Wæther is a weather display app. Its main feature is that it gets its weather information from the Norwegian Meteorological Institute. 

Features:
- Celsius or Fahrenheit;
- forecast for the next days (mostly 10 days);
- up to 2 favorite locations + current location (gps-based);
- Wind speed (mps) and direction + sunrise and sunset time (by pressing the select button)
- Rain precipitation (mm)
Data from The Norwegian Meteorological institute. Names for geolocating provided by Google. Symbols provided by yr.no.

I'd appreciate any feedback with suggestions of improvement - and if you use it, please "like it" here and I'd be happy if you consider a $1 donation.

